 "remarks": "Enjoy the ultimate walk-to-town lifestyle from this bright and spacious 2-bedroom, 2 bath townhouse, in a quiet, private setting just moments from the heart of Westport. The sun-filled living room features hardwood floors and flows seamlessly into an open kitchen with a breakfast bar, dining area, and direct access to a private patio-perfect for morning coffee or a little fresh air. Upstairs, you&apos;ll find two generously sized bedrooms and a full bath. Set just off the beaten path, this charming and well-maintained complex offers carefree living with desirable amenities including an elevator, covered garage parking, and a prime central location. Stroll over the Saugatuck River bridge to Westport&apos;s renowned restaurants, fantastic shops in a lively, and vibrant downtown. Commuters and outdoor enthusiasts alike will appreciate the close proximity to the train station, Longshore, and the beach. A wonderful opportunity to enjoy all that Westport has to offer!",
